<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[437, 163, 561, 182]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 196, 240, 213]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 226, 384, 245]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\),

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[420, 245, 584, 280]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}.\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 312, 230, 330]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[243, 335, 755, 371]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1} b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2} b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r} b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 382, 500, 415]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\).

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[401, 481, 596, 500]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 543, 576, 562]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 568, 576, 588]]<|/det|>
\[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[413, 593, 584, 613]]<|/det|>
\[\csc \mathrm{e}^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 642, 243, 660]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[406, 664, 591, 694]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[403, 715, 593, 735]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc \cos A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[438, 744, 559, 772]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc \sin A\]
